name: Ronnie Fieg x New Balance 577 'Americana'
description: The Ronnie Fieg for New Balance 577 "Americana" seen in a full pigskin upper, featuring texture characteristics that are reminiscent of denim in Indigo and Slate coloring. 3M hits are added to the "N" leather side patch that uses an off-white leather backing, the toe panel and the heel wrap. Final details include red accenting throughout, indigo lining, "KITH" and "NEW BALANCE" printed on the in-soles and stitched "NB" and "577" patches on the tongue, while below sits a speckled ENCAP midsole and a bold red outsole. Each pair comes with a Red/White/Blue rope lace, Navy lace and Red lace. Extra lace features include "RF" and "NB" lace locks, and "KITH RF NB" printed on the Navy lace aglets and on the top of the Red laces.

name: Jordan 12 'Taxi'
description:
***This is a Pre-order***
Item will be shipped once received

A true classic is back. The Air Jordan 12 Retro ‘Taxi’ returns in its original colorway, launched in the season of MJ’s fifth championship (’96-’97). It features a white, tumbled-leather upper with stitching that mimics the rays of the rising sun. Taxi gold pops on the lace stays and black leather finishes the upper. A touch of Varsity Red peeks through the solid black outsole and the “23” on the heel strip.

name: Kobe Prelude 1
description:
***This is a Pre-Order***
Will send out once received w/ Copy of original Receipt.

INSPIRED BY KOBE'S SUPERNATURAL PERFORMANCE

Born from the supernatural performance of Kobe's 81-point game, the Nike Zoom Kobe Prelude I embraces surrealist artistry that brings the guts of a mamba to the surface. With it, we get a glimpse into the heart of a true competitor and see the beginnings of Kobe going lower with each shoe.

BENEFITS

Rich, full-grain leather upper for a premium fit and durable feel
Padded and breathable ankle collar for support and comfort
Phylon midsole for lightweight cushioning
Midfoot flex grooves for multidirectional flexibility
Nike Zoom for low-profile cushioning and lightweight performance
Full-length exposed carbon fiber spring plate for multidirectional force and speed
Durable, lightweight solid rubber outsole with herringbone pattern for traction

A ROAD TO THE MASTERPIECE

The Kobe Prelude Pack celebrates the stories behind some of Kobe's most defining moments. Eight revolutionary art movements have been paired with eight milestones in Kobe's career to recreate each of Kobe's signature shoes.
